snippet: At 23, Coco Rocha is already beginning to age out of the modeling business. But that’s fine with her (and her 400,000 Twitter followers).
abstract: Profile of model Coco Rocha, who at 23 is beginning to age out of the business; she is speaking out about the pressure the fashion industry puts on young models, and is coaching up-and-coming models on building a following through social media; Rocha became the first model to surpass one million followers on Google Plus and has reached an additional two million fans on Weibo, China's version of Twitter.
lead_paragraph: At 23, Coco Rocha is already beginning to age out of the modeling business. But that’s fine with her (and her 400,000 Twitter followers).

headline.seo: Coco Rocha, Expanding Her Efforts To Be a Role Model
